{"tid":2350758,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭：國安法草擬期間港府給予很多意見","createTime":"2021-01-02T14:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-02T17:02:23.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1459b89f31afbbd12dde43a7e7718a5d029520","tid":2350758,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥在facebook上載與行政會議召集人陳智思對談的短片，當中提及有關《港區國安法》的制訂。林鄭月娥表示，當知悉中央決定立《港區國安法》時，港府成立核心小組，成員包括她、律政司長鄭若驊及保安局局長李家超，於《港區國安法》草擬過程期間給予很多意見，「我今日可以講，中央非常重視我們的意見」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，中央只是劃清楚底線，而要求亦不算高，包括維護國家安全，保障領土完整，希望在社會有廣泛宣傳和教育，認識國家安全的重要性。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥認為，《港區國安法》訂立後，立竿見影的效果是「香港真的平伏了」，再無以往的暴亂事件。她亦指出，《港區國安法》包括不少法律原則，例如一罪不能兩審、未判之前假設無罪、公開審訊等都有保留。"},{"pid":"879e308808d82271543310a94797bd7003bf288c","tid":2350758,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:23:10.000Z","msg":"港奸自證"},{"pid":"08d58d33f3c43df5ab1c789db23187ab9782b051","tid":2350758,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:29:49.000Z","msg":"咁樣玩攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a35ee19dced74f603a9a76c9c9b563ee70b3e1","tid":2350758,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:31:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"837053fb63ea8bc812a3af226b8f43ad5cafe678","tid":2350758,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"包括植物人先可以保釋？"},{"pid":"56cd778dc23ced4558d4cb780ac61a8edb7c2717","tid":2350758,"uid":305358,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T15:39:16.000Z","msg":"唔怪得要制裁你，抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/catxm/swipe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0fd2fdacec4793dc698b6